eventdef-speechsynthesisutterance-start.summary: The start event of the Web Speech API SpeechSynthesisUtterance object is fired when the utterance has begun to be spoken.
eventdef-speechsynthesisutterance-start.title: SpeechSynthesisUtterance: start event

dom-speechsynthesisutterance-onstart.name: start_event
dom-speechsynthesisutterance-onstart.summary: The start event of the Web Speech API SpeechSynthesisUtterance object is fired when the utterance has begun to be spoken.
dom-speechsynthesisutterance-onstart.title: SpeechSynthesisUtterance: start event

dom-speechsynthesisutterance-text.name: text
dom-speechsynthesisutterance-text.summary: The text property of the SpeechSynthesisUtterance interface gets and sets the text that will be synthesized when the utterance is spoken.
dom-speechsynthesisutterance-text.title: SpeechSynthesisUtterance: text property

dom-speechsynthesisutterance-voice.name: voice
dom-speechsynthesisutterance-voice.summary: The voice property of the SpeechSynthesisUtterance interface gets and sets the voice that will be used to speak the utterance.
dom-speechsynthesisutterance-voice.title: SpeechSynthesisUtterance: voice property

dom-speechsynthesisutterance-volume.name: volume
dom-speechsynthesisutterance-volume.summary: The volume property of the SpeechSynthesisUtterance interface gets and sets the volume that the utterance will be spoken at.
dom-speechsynthesisutterance-volume.title: SpeechSynthesisUtterance: volume property

speechsynthesisutterance.name: SpeechSynthesisUtterance
speechsynthesisutterance.summary: The SpeechSynthesisUtterance interface of the Web Speech API represents a speech request. It contains the content the speech service should read and information about how to read it (e.g. language, pitch and volume.)
speechsynthesisutterance.title: SpeechSynthesisUtterance

dom-speechsynthesisvoice-default.name: default
dom-speechsynthesisvoice-default.summary: The default read-only property of the SpeechSynthesisVoice interface returns a boolean value indicating whether the voice is the default voice for the current app (true), or not (false.)
dom-speechsynthesisvoice-default.title: SpeechSynthesisVoice: default property

dom-speechsynthesisvoice-lang.name: lang
dom-speechsynthesisvoice-lang.summary: The lang read-only property of the SpeechSynthesisVoice interface returns a BCP 47 language tag indicating the language of the voice.
dom-speechsynthesisvoice-lang.title: SpeechSynthesisVoice: lang property

dom-speechsynthesisvoice-localservice.name: localService
dom-speechsynthesisvoice-localservice.summary: The localService read-only property of the SpeechSynthesisVoice interface returns a boolean value indicating whether the voice is supplied by a local speech synthesizer service (true), or a remote speech synthesizer service (false.)
dom-speechsynthesisvoice-localservice.title: SpeechSynthesisVoice: localService property

dom-speechsynthesisvoice-name.name: name
dom-speechsynthesisvoice-name.summary: The name read-only property of the SpeechSynthesisVoice interface returns a human-readable name that represents the voice.
dom-speechsynthesisvoice-name.title: SpeechSynthesisVoice: name property

dom-speechsynthesisvoice-voiceuri.name: voiceURI
dom-speechsynthesisvoice-voiceuri.summary: The voiceURI read-only property of the SpeechSynthesisVoice interface returns the type of URI and location of the speech synthesis service for this voice.
dom-speechsynthesisvoice-voiceuri.title: SpeechSynthesisVoice: voiceURI property

speechsynthesisvoice.name: SpeechSynthesisVoice
speechsynthesisvoice.summary: The SpeechSynthesisVoice interface of the Web Speech API represents a voice that the system supports. Every SpeechSynthesisVoice has its own relative speech service including information about language, name and URI.

firefox.notes: In Firefox, speech synthesis voices do not start loading until after the first call to window.speechSynthesis.getVoices(). A way to mitigate this issue is to call the method at the beginning of page load, then wait a few seconds before calling the method again. Voices will remain loaded until all tabs that have called this method have been closed.

speechsynthesisvoice.title: SpeechSynthesisVoice
